$LNG['CONDITION_43']			= 'Our websites are optimized for navigation via a desktop computer or laptop. Therefore, we can not guarantee the availability and flow of our services on other media such as smartphones and tablets.<br /><br />        The user must have the latest stable version of its web browser to join and use our services.       In addition, it must have a web browsers compatible with our platforms, including the complete list :       <ul>         <li>Mozilla Firefox</li>         <li>Google Chrome</li>       </ul>        Our company will not be held liable for bugs and errors in the case of non-compliance with these requirements.';
$LNG['CONDITION_44']			= 'Although Antaris Legacy should ensure that all its services are working properly, it is possible that certain situations or circumstances are beyond our control. They can lead to a momentary stop or malfunction for a undeterminded time. Thus, the user can have no claims for the proper functioning of the benefits and services provided by Antaris Legacy.<br /><br />        Antaris Legacy can not be held responsible for a malfunction on one of its servers or bad programming (this is only one example among others).<br /><br />         Nevertheless, the Antaris Legacy Staff will make every effort to resolve as quickly as possible any faults of its services.';
$LNG['CONDITION_45']			= 'All the services we provide, including accounts and items in its accounts are the property of Antaris Legacy.       They are put at disposal of the players.<br /><br />        The items available to users are virtual items. Actual transactions on an account are therefore prohibited       (For example, a donation account in exchange for material goods is strictly prohibited).<br /><br />        A user account is not transferable without the express approval of Antaris Legacy or its representatives.';
$LNG['CONDITION_46']			= 'When a player registers on the game or on the forum, he must accept the conditions here present.<br /><br />        A membership is only possible for human individuals. Permission for use is only as individuals (not groups, families, etc ...).       If the user is 13 or under 13 year, it must guarantee to be in possession of a valid permit from his legal representative.<br /><br />        Upon registration, the user must specify a player name and a valid email address. Antaris Legacy reserve the right to verify the validity at any time and take the necessary steps in case of disability.<br /><br />        The email address is used to identify an owner in case of loss of connection data.       Therefore, it is impossible to transmit a report to the owner if the email address is invalid.<br /><br />              When you join, you authorize Antaris Legacy to send you its newsletter. However, you can unsubscribe from it by clicking the link unsubscribe which is at the bottom of each « NewsLetter » email.';
$LNG['CONDITION_47']			= 'The user can choose not to use the services provided by Antaris Legacy. For this, he can remove his or her accounts of our game platforms.       Deleting accounts automatically result in the termination of these conditions. However, this deletion may be delayed for technical issues.<br /><br />              The user automatically accepts, and powerless against it, the termination of this contract in the absence of over 90 days (no connection to our server).       Nevertheless, there are several exceptions that cancel deletion after inactivity : the account is paused or you have made at least a purchase on the game.<br /><br />              Antaris Legacy reserves the right to give an account after a résilitation through an automatic donation system.       When the system performs this donation, all the users personal data such as email addresses, IP addresses and messages are deleted permanently.';
$LNG['CONDITION_48']			= 'If the user does not comply with these terms and conditions and/or settlement of the game when using our services, then Antaris Legacy reserves the right to delete or block (s) account (s) of the user, without this excluded the possibility of additional sanctions.      The account deletion is decided by the administrator or by one of the moderators of the service in question (under the game regulations, general conditions and French law).<br /><br />        Any claims for the account of erasure can be brought to the forum (in the section provided for this purpose).       There can be no legal claims for closing an account.        The company may decide at any time to suspend all of its services and to delete all accounts.       For this, a member of the company must first notify users of the termination of their accounts via a message visible on the site of Antaris Legacy.       In the latter case, the minimum period between the announcement of closure and suspension of services (and therefore, the removal of accounts) is one month.';
$LNG['CONDITION_49']			= 'Si l\'utilisateur en fait la demande, il peut être remboursé dans les 14 jours qui ont suivi son ou ses achats Paypal (valable uniquement sur les achats effectués auprès de notre société,       via le mode paiement « Paypal »). Si vous souhaitez être remboursé des achats effectués via Allopass, vous devez les contacter par vos propres moyens afin d\'avoir un remboursement.       Bien entendu, les services obtenus par le biais de ces achats seront retirés de votre compte.<br /><br />        Au delà de ce délai, aucun remboursement ne sera effectué par l\'entreprise, même dans le cas d\'une résiliation.       En effet, lorsqu\'un utilisateur accepte une dépense, alors celle-ci ne lui donne pas le droit de demander un remboursement à la suite d\'une résiliation par l\'utilisateur ou par l\'entreprise.<br /><br />        Enfin, un utilisateur ne peut pas demander à être remboursé suite à un bug ou à une erreur qui est survenu sur un de nos services.       Cependant, nous mettrons tout en oeuvre pour corriger les bugs contastés dans les plus brefs délais selon nos disponibilités.       En tant qu\'auto-entrepeneur, il est possible que ces délais soient de l\'ordre de plusieurs semaines pour les plus gros bugs.';
$LNG['CONDITION_50']			= 'When an account is funded in part by a user through Pay extensions, one has access to this why he paid : he can claim nothing more than the extension he bought.<br /><br />              We remind that all purchases made on this website are only virtual, and they do not give any additional rights to the user with respect to a « lambda » user who have not bought extensions.';
$LNG['CONDITION_51']			= 'Antaris Legacy is a game, so we set up a platform to put players in relationship.       Only the user is responsible for what he wishes for others. Our company can not be held responsible.       Thus, about pornographic, xenophobic, insulting or illegal content are not permitted and are the civil and/or criminal perpetrators.<br /><br />        However, the moderation and administration strives to erase and remove offending sentence from users.      Moreover, Antaris Legacy reserves the right to block and/or delete the accounts of those users without notice.       These sanctions do not exclude any civil and/or criminal prosecution, if the company deems necessary.<br /><br />              Similarly, the company can not be held responsible for illegal about any of its volunteer representatives (eg moderation).';
$LNG['CONDITION_52']			= 'Antaris Legacy is not liable for damages, regardless of the severity, caused by the use of one of our services.       The company reminds players that the excessive use of video or computer games can cause severe physical and/or mental disabilities.
       Each user is assumed to have knowledge of, and therefore accepts the risks.';
$LNG['CONDITION_53']			= 'Piracy is punishable by law. Any hacking or hacking attempts is liable to prosecution. This may relate to piracy services and corporate servers, but also for user accounts. Any attempt or hacking will result in sanctions such as blocking of the account or the offending IP address. Criminal penalties for cybercrime can be up to 5 years imprisonment and a 75,000 euro forfeit.<br /><br />        Antaris Legacy has set up a data encryption system. Therefore, hacking a player account can only be due to a password too easy to hack (or it is too short or the password is too simple). We advise you not to use the words of everyday life, but rather to compose a password with letters and numbers with no meaning.<br /><br />        The user undertakes to keep strictly confidential hes login credentials.       It also requires to only enter the login credentials on the website pages operated by Antaris Legacy.       Thus, we strongly recommend the user to verify that it is on the right authentication page before filling his access code when logging.<br /><br />        In the case of non-compliance with any of the conditions described above, the company can not be held responsible for any theft or account hacking, and their consequences.';
$LNG['CONDITION_54']			= 'The user has no right to perform actions that slow down the Antaris Legacy site, either through a script or something else.       He has not the right to block the site, modify or restate the content, or other official content redirected by Antaris Legacy Member without prior permission from the administrator.';
$LNG['CONDITION_55']			= 'It is strictly forbidden to use programs other than a standard browser to browse our site (use and visualization).       Antaris Legacy means particularly all scripts or programs called « Bot » that can perform actions automatically.       The use of any add-ons and script to simplify, facilitate, and replace a human is forbidden and will result in heavy penalties.<br /><br />              To limit cheating on the game Antaris Legacy, the use of VPN/proxy or other program to hide the origin and/or IP address of the user is prohibited.       The access to the game is not recommended for all persons wishing to keep their confidential information.';
$LNG['CONDITION_56']			= 'It is strictly forbidden for a user to impersonate a member of the company or a member belonging to the Antaris Legacy moderation.       The « virtual » impersonation one team member brings a definitive and automatic banishment of our services.';
