$LNG['CONDITION_58']			= 'The user can create only one account per universe, otherwise what will be considered a non-regulatory Client.       The above rule applies to all of our universe, but it can be legalized by a staff member (read the rules to learn more).       The non-regulatory multi-accounts can be sanctioned without notice by various means : warning, suspension of the offending accounts and/or deletion of accounts.';
$LNG['CONDITION_59']			= 'When a player registered with one of our universe, on one of our sites or on the forum, he must accept the general conditions (the present) and the regulations of service to which it adheres. Therefore, he knows all the general rules and conditions as it has read them and accepted.';
$LNG['CONDITION_61']			= 'Following the non-compliance with the game rules or general conditions, the user can be blocked temporarily or permanently.       Blocking can be valid on a part or all of the services offered by Antaris Legacy.';
$LNG['CONDITION_62']			= 'Antaris Legacy backup your personal data in order to verify compliance with the game rules and general conditions.       This data can be technical (IP address, login time, browser used, operating system, e-mail address provided during registration), but they can also be a statistical one (number of purchases, age, sex) or even personal.<br /><br />        These data could be provided either at the request of the company when creating the account, or, where applicable, provided voluntarily by the user.<br /><br />              Antaris Legacy makes every effort to save your personal data securely. However, the company can not be held responsible for the leak of this data in case of hacking of one of its services.';
$LNG['CONDITION_63']			= 'Antaris Legacy reserves the right to communicate all of these data to the French authorities in order to protect its interests or in the event of possible breaches of statutory provisions.';
$LNG['CONDITION_64']			= 'Nous rappelons à nos utilisateurs que, pour le respect de la protection de leurs données personnelles, détaillé dans le présent paragraphe,       Antaris Legacy est enregistrée à la CNIL sous le numéro 1 538 743 (Fichiers clients-prospects) et le numéro 1 538 741 (Traitements statistiques).';
$LNG['CONDITION_65']			= 'You can ask Antaris Legacy to provide all personal data about you, for this, please contact us via the following email address : staff@antaris-legacy.co.       If you request removal of your personal data, this will automatically result in the deletion and termination of all of your user accounts.';
$LNG['CONDITION_66']			= 'Antaris Legacy uses Google Analytics, a web analytics service provided by Google Inc. (Google).<br /><br />        Google Analytics uses cookies, which are text files placed on your computer to help the website analyze site usage by its users.       The data generated by the cookie about your use of the website (including your IP address) is transmitted and stored by Google on servers in the United States.<br /><br />              Google will use this information to evaluate your use of the website, compiling reports on website activity to Antaris Legacy and providing other services relating to website activity and Internet use.<br /><br />              Google may also transfer this information to third parties where required by law or where such third parties process the information on Google behalf, including in particular the editor of this site. Google will not cut your IP address with other Google data.<br /><br />        You can disable the use of cookies by selecting the appropriate settings on your browser. However, this deactivation could prevent the use of some features of this website.       Using Antaris Legacy platforms, you consent to the processing of data by Google in the manner and for the purposes described above.';
$LNG['CONDITION_67']			= 'Your personal data will naturally not be sold to third parties. However, Antaris Legacy transmit to third parties personal data provided by you, besides the use of Google Analytics, only in the following cases : Payment service providers (PayPal, AlloPass), host (OVH). These service providers have access to your personal data in the limit allowing them to perform their tasks.       These providers are required to process your personal data in accordance with this declaration of personal data protection and the basic laws governing data protection.';
$LNG['CONDITION_68']			= 'All accounts are the property of Antaris Legacy. It is the same for all the elements in it (the accounts) such as resources, units, buildings, technologies, etc ...       No rights, in particular those concerning the operation, can be granted to the user.';
$LNG['CONDITION_69']			= 'In general, without the written permission of the company, it is prohibited to contract with a third party any agreement on the transfer, use or storage of personal data or accounts. So it is particularly prohibited to sell accounts or resources (or other component of an account) or to make a profit by leaving accounts (or one of its components) in favor of a third party :       indeed, it is still owned by Antaris Legacy and therefore can not make the object of an transaction.<br /><br />        The same prohibitions apply to personal data and rights of use.       Is particularly relevant here, any transaction against Allopass, or anything of value.<br /><br />        Violation of these rules or any other right of society, particularly those concerning copyrights, will be forwarded to the authorities and confirmed by civil and/or criminal. Additional penalties may also be taken by the company, including the blocking of all the offending user accounts.';
